row.Title: The Spurs’ Bench Could Probably Make The Playoffs On Its Own FiveThirtyEight
row.Selection: The 2015-16 Golden State Warriors are an all-time great team — you know this, everyone knows this. But as impressive as they are, the Dubs have been outplayed by a couple of NBA units so far this season: the San Antonio Spurs’ starters — and the San Antonio Spurs’ bench.
